# ATOWA Conseil - Intelligent Agri Advisor
A Progressive Web App (PWA) empowering African farmers with offline weather, AI advice, and image analysis.  
- **Prototype**: https://atowa-agri-advisor-ai.lovable.app  
- **Future**: AtowaFi for financial services  
